nodes.text: A human female served as a member of Emperor Palpatine's Royal Guard. She once knew Lando Calrissian, a smuggler from Socorro. Upon inspecting the corrupted corpses of two Royal Guards aboard the luxury pleasure craft Imperialis, Calrissian evoked this Royal Guard, noting that she looked nothing like the deceased Guardsman. Korin Pers, an associate of Calrissian's, assumed that she and Calrissian were once romantically involved.
